Title: Round 2: Kang Bramblestaff
Description:
Your next challenger is a Bramblestaff. Strength is in their blood. I remember a full century of only Bramblestaff champions.

No pressure, little $r.

Go to the eastern arena north of here and face this young challenger. See first hand if strength is earned or inherited.
PortraitGiverText: The Bramblestaff family have long held the championship.
